# Key finding: decimal.Decimal.__pow__ is true (supports ** exponentiation);
# decimal.Decimal.__lshift__ and __rshift__ are false (bitwise shifts are
# integer-only operations). All other decimal classes are false for all three.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

